282
00:15:51,414 --> 00:15:53,054
That's why I was harsh with my words.

283
00:15:54,493 --> 00:15:55,333
How about this?

284
00:15:55,654 --> 00:15:57,654
Go and rest in Changqiu Palace.

285
00:15:58,134 --> 00:15:59,294
