369
00:23:09,614 --> 00:23:11,213
Not anymore.

370
00:23:13,973 --> 00:23:15,334
I wish General Wan

371
00:23:16,053 --> 00:23:17,574
to return with victory.

372
00:23:17,693 --> 00:23:18,773
Thank you.

373
00:23:41,094 --> 00:23:42,374
I wish General Wan

374
00:23:42,814 --> 00:23:44,293
